1
00:00:38,574 --> 00:00:40,826
<i>Kule mbali milimani,</i>

2
00:00:43,204 --> 00:00:45,497
<i>Teletubbies wanakuja kucheza.</i>

3
00:00:45,498 --> 00:00:47,541
<i>- Moja.
- Moja.</i>

4
00:00:47,542 --> 00:00:49,918
<i>- Mbili.
- Mbili!</i>

5
00:00:49,919 --> 00:00:52,672
<i>- Tatu.
- Tatu!</i>

6
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:56,300
<i>- Nne!
- Nne!</i>

7
00:00:57,718 --> 00:01:01,012
<i>Na Teletubbies
wanapendana sana.</i>

8
00:01:01,013 --> 00:01:02,640
<i>Ooh.</i>

9
00:01:03,516 --> 00:01:05,226
<i>Kumbatio kubwa.</i>

10
00:01:15,403 --> 00:01:17,028
Hairuhusiwi.
Kwa nini umechelewa hivi?

11
00:01:17,029 --> 00:01:18,154
Hawapiti hapa.

12
00:01:18,155 --> 00:01:19,656
Haijalishi, haijalishi!

13
00:01:19,657 --> 00:01:21,783
Wako wapi wengine?
Walikuwa nyuma yangu kabisa.

14
00:01:21,784 --> 00:01:23,201
<i>- Muda wa Teletubbies.</i>
- Tuwapeleke watoto wote kwenye gari moja.

15
00:01:23,202 --> 00:01:24,370
<i>Muda wa Teletubbies.</i>

16
00:01:26,038 --> 00:01:28,081
Keti hapa. Keti!

17
00:01:28,082 --> 00:01:29,499
Shangazi, kuna nini?

18
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:32,794
Jimmy, tulia, nyamaza,
na usiondoke hapa.

19
00:01:32,795 --> 00:01:35,213
Lazima tuwaingize watoto kwenye gari!

20
00:01:35,214 --> 00:01:37,048
Ulikuwa unafanya nini?
Nilikuambia ufanye haraka!

21
00:01:37,049 --> 00:01:38,551
Mungu wangu!

22
00:01:43,181 --> 00:01:44,182
Jimmy?

23
00:01:50,605 --> 00:01:51,689
Nini kile?

24
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,485
<i>Teletubbies wameenda wapi?</i>

25
00:02:04,744 --> 00:02:05,745
Baba?

26
00:02:07,996 --> 00:02:09,623
<i>- Tinky Winky.
- Tinky Winky.</i>

27
00:02:09,624 --> 00:02:10,833
<i>Dipsy.</i>

28
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:23,470
Jimmy, kimbia.

29
00:02:23,471 --> 00:02:25,890
 - Mama?
- Kimbia! Kimbia!

30
00:02:34,357 --> 00:02:35,358
Kimbia!

31
00:02:36,192 --> 00:02:38,109
Kimbia! Jimmy, kimbia!

32
00:02:38,110 --> 00:02:39,487
Nenda!

33
00:02:43,783 --> 00:02:45,284
Baba! Baba!

34
00:02:52,917 --> 00:02:54,001
Baba!

35
00:03:00,550 --> 00:03:01,968
Baba!

36
00:03:02,802 --> 00:03:03,885
Baba!

37
00:03:03,886 --> 00:03:05,971
- Jimmy. - Baba.

38
00:03:05,972 --> 00:03:07,848
Baba, nini kinatokea?

39
00:03:07,849 --> 00:03:10,559
Hakuna ambalo halijatabiriwa kwa ukamilifu.

40
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:13,270
Ninaogopa sana, Baba. Nadhani Mama na dada huenda wamekufa.

41
00:03:13,271 --> 00:03:15,231
Hapana, mwanangu.

42
00:03:16,107 --> 00:03:17,108
Hawajafa.

43
00:03:17,692 --> 00:03:18,901
Wameokolewa.

44
00:03:20,236 --> 00:03:21,821
Kwani hii ni siku ya utukufu.

45
00:03:22,738 --> 00:03:24,031
Siku ya hukumu.

46
00:03:29,203 --> 00:03:31,122
Chukua, mwanangu.

47
00:03:34,625 --> 00:03:36,335
Kaa na hiki kila wakati.

48
00:03:38,087 --> 00:03:39,589
Kuwa na imani.

49
00:03:43,050 --> 00:03:44,510
Ndiyo.

50
00:03:45,595 --> 00:03:46,596
Ndiyo.

51
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,015
Ndiyo, wanangu!

52
00:03:50,391 --> 00:03:51,767
Ndiyo!

53
00:04:04,197 --> 00:04:07,533
Ndiyo!

54
00:04:13,998 --> 00:04:14,999
Baba...

55
00:04:15,666 --> 00:04:17,251
mbona umeniacha?

56
00:05:05,049 --> 00:05:09,206
Manukuu yametolewa na: Aren Zohrabi

57
00:05:34,662 --> 00:05:35,830
Ni siku yako kubwa, Spike.

58
00:05:37,456 --> 00:05:38,624
Amka sasa.

59
00:07:16,305 --> 00:07:17,306
Tutaonana baadaye.

60
00:07:32,989 --> 00:07:34,364
Una tochi yako?

61
00:07:34,365 --> 00:07:35,658
Sweta, kipenga...

62
00:07:36,534 --> 00:07:37,535
chupa ya maji?

63
00:07:38,995 --> 00:07:40,079
Chukua.

64
00:07:42,039 --> 00:07:43,124
Una kisu chako?

65
00:07:44,834 --> 00:07:45,835
Kijana mzuri.

66
00:07:53,426 --> 00:07:54,427
Weka mbali hicho.

67
00:07:59,307 --> 00:08:01,725
Tunakula bekoni? Kwa kiamsha kinywa?

68
00:08:01,726 --> 00:08:03,644
Dave na Rosey\nwalileta jana usiku.

69
00:08:07,106 --> 00:08:08,273
Chako kiko wapi?

70
00:08:08,274 --> 00:08:09,816
Nimeshakula tayari, nilipokuwa nikipika.

71
00:08:09,817 --> 00:08:10,902
Haya, sawa.

72
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:15,780
Spikey.

73
00:08:15,781 --> 00:08:17,074
Ni chako chote.

74
00:08:31,255 --> 00:08:32,714
Nitakwenda kumwangalia mama yako.

75
00:08:32,715 --> 00:08:33,798
Malizia.

76
00:08:34,634 --> 00:08:36,009
Weka sahani yako pembeni.

77
00:08:42,141 --> 00:08:43,142
Naja, mpenzi.

78
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,645
Chukua, mpenzi.

79
00:08:46,771 --> 00:08:47,813
Kuna nini, nini mbaya?

80
00:08:53,778 --> 00:08:56,405
- Jamie...\n- Inabidi uvumilie, mpenzi.

81
00:08:57,073 --> 00:09:00,409
- Inabidi ubaki hapa upumzike.\n- Oh, siwezi. Hapana.

82
00:09:01,035 --> 00:09:02,285
Oh, Spikey.

83
00:09:02,286 --> 00:09:03,703
Mambo, Mama.

84
00:09:03,704 --> 00:09:05,498
Oh, mwanangu.

85
00:09:06,457 --> 00:09:09,709
Unajua, sikutaka kuleta usumbufu.\nNi kichwa changu. Ni...

86
00:09:09,710 --> 00:09:11,546
- Ni sawa.\n- Kinagonga tu.

87
00:09:12,672 --> 00:09:15,216
Oh, mbona usiniambie\nshule ilikuwaje leo?

88
00:09:16,843 --> 00:09:18,261
Sijaenda shule, Mama.

89
00:09:18,803 --> 00:09:19,804
Ni asubuhi.

90
00:09:21,097 --> 00:09:22,849
- Kweli?\n- Ndiyo...

91
00:09:23,808 --> 00:09:25,184
ni asubuhi, na...

92
00:09:26,352 --> 00:09:27,353
Isla...

93
00:09:28,229 --> 00:09:29,230
unakumbuka?

94
00:09:29,939 --> 00:09:31,439
Spike haendi shule leo.

95
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,525
Kwa nini?

96
00:09:34,694 --> 00:09:36,278
Tayari ni wikendi?

97
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,655
Hapana, ni Ijumaa.

98
00:09:39,824 --> 00:09:41,492
Sasa kwa nini haendi shule?

99
00:09:43,035 --> 00:09:44,203
Tuliongea kuhusu hili.

100
00:09:45,663 --> 00:09:48,124
- Mara chache.
- Tuliongea kuhusu nini, Jamie?

101
00:09:48,749 --> 00:09:50,877
Mimi na Spike tunaenda nje.

102
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:53,170
Ni mara yake ya kwanza.

103
00:09:53,171 --> 00:09:54,588
Mara ya kwanza?

104
00:09:54,589 --> 00:09:58,300
Unamaanisha mnatoka kisiwani,
mnaenda bara?

105
00:09:58,301 --> 00:10:00,135
- Ndiyo.
- Nini?

106
00:10:00,136 --> 00:10:02,554
- Isla.
- Unazungumzia upuuzi gani huu?

107
00:10:02,555 --> 00:10:05,349
- Haya. Usitukane. Haya basi.
- Umerukwa na akili nini?

108
00:10:05,933 --> 00:10:06,933
Ni mtoto mchanga huyu!

109
00:10:06,934 --> 00:10:08,185
- Mama...
- Ana miaka kumi na miwili.

110
00:10:08,186 --> 00:10:10,312
Unajaribu kumuua
mtoto wetu, wewe mshenzi?

111
00:10:10,313 --> 00:10:11,521
Spike, rudi
chini, tafadhali?

112
00:10:11,522 --> 00:10:14,065
- Wewe ni mwuaji wa watoto mwendawazimu.
- Hapana, Baba, wewe nenda chini.

113
00:10:14,066 --> 00:10:15,442
- Kama babangu angekuwa hapa...
- Hapana, nakwambia.

114
00:10:15,443 --> 00:10:17,694
- angekuchuna ngozi ukiwa hai, mwuaji wa watoto!
- Itakuwa bora ikiwa... Haya basi!

115
00:10:17,695 --> 00:10:19,487
- Mshenzi!
- Haya. Isla, imetosha.

116
00:10:19,488 --> 00:10:20,739
- Fala!
- Haya. Atakuwa sawa.

117
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:21,908
Pumbavu!

118
00:10:22,867 --> 00:10:24,285
- Mama...
- Hapana.

119
00:10:25,036 --> 00:10:26,037
Ni mimi.

120
00:10:28,956 --> 00:10:31,042
Spike... Spikey.

121
00:10:31,709 --> 00:10:33,377
Kuna nini? Naona joto.

122
00:10:34,253 --> 00:10:36,171
Mbona nahisi joto hivi?

123
00:10:36,172 --> 00:10:37,756
Ni hali ya hewa tu, Mama.

124
00:10:37,757 --> 00:10:38,966
Joto sana.

125
00:10:40,301 --> 00:10:41,302
Ni sawa.

126
00:10:44,847 --> 00:10:46,474
Nimekuletea kiamsha kinywa.

127
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,685
Ni kipande cha bekoni.

128
00:10:51,354 --> 00:10:52,605
Kula kidogo utakapojisikia.

129
00:10:55,650 --> 00:10:56,691
Unatoka? Santuri? (Unatoka?)

130
00:10:56,692 --> 00:10:58,611
- Ndiyo.\n- Wapi?

131
00:11:00,321 --> 00:11:01,322
Shuleni.

132
00:11:05,826 --> 00:11:07,077
Sawa, Spikey.

133
00:11:07,078 --> 00:11:08,371
Oh, nakupenda.

134
00:11:10,414 --> 00:11:11,666
Pia nakupenda, Mama.

135
00:11:17,046 --> 00:11:18,213
Habari za asubuhi, kijana.

136
00:11:18,214 --> 00:11:19,298
Sam.

137
00:11:19,882 --> 00:11:21,384
Nimekutengenezea kamba hii upya.

138
00:11:22,969 --> 00:11:24,010
Ilihitaji kamba mpya?

139
00:11:24,011 --> 00:11:26,638
Hapana. Nimefanya kwa ajili yangu tu, kweli.

140
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,015
Atakuwa sawa, Sam.

141
00:11:29,016 --> 00:11:31,185
Vuta, mwanangu. Hisi uzito.

142
00:11:35,314 --> 00:11:36,315
Ishike.

143
00:11:36,983 --> 00:11:38,693
Haitikisiki hata kidogo.

144
00:11:39,277 --> 00:11:40,444
Kijana shupavu.

145
00:11:41,737 --> 00:11:43,322
Haya basi, mwanangu. Twende.

146
00:11:50,204 --> 00:11:52,622
Sawa. Sawa.

147
00:11:52,623 --> 00:11:53,916
Tutaonana usiku.

148
00:11:54,375 --> 00:11:56,376
- Maisha yako hatarini.\n- Asanteni, vijana.

149
00:11:56,377 --> 00:11:57,753
- Haya basi, Jamie!\n- Kila la heri, Spike.

150
00:11:58,546 --> 00:12:00,422
- Nimefurahi unaendelea vyema sasa, Spike.\n- Haya, Spike!

151
00:12:00,423 --> 00:12:02,008
Safari njema, kijana.

152
00:12:06,888 --> 00:12:08,347
Hii imetoka kwa Mama.

153
00:12:09,682 --> 00:12:12,142
- Asante, Betty.
- Sherehe yako kubwa ni leo, Spike wetu.

154
00:12:12,143 --> 00:12:13,352
Usichelewe!

155
00:12:14,145 --> 00:12:15,562
Mrejeshe salama, sawa?

156
00:12:15,563 --> 00:12:16,939
Haya, Jamie!

157
00:12:27,116 --> 00:12:28,409
Mwangalie, Jamie!

158
00:12:30,244 --> 00:12:32,538
- Kila la heri, Spike.
- Sawa, Jacob.

159
00:12:43,841 --> 00:12:44,926
Tazama hiyo, Spike.

160
00:12:45,676 --> 00:12:47,093
Kamati nzima ya uongozi ipo hapa.

161
00:12:47,094 --> 00:12:49,222
Tabasamu tu na uwe na adabu.

162
00:12:49,805 --> 00:12:51,224
Ilibidi nije kukuaga.

163
00:12:51,933 --> 00:12:53,600
Sote tuna furaha kwa ajili yako.

164
00:12:53,601 --> 00:12:55,560
Ingawa unajua
nahisi bado ni mdogo sana.

165
00:12:55,561 --> 00:12:58,063
Miaka kumi na nne au kumi na tano
ndiyo inafaa zaidi kulingana na taratibu.

166
00:12:58,064 --> 00:12:59,356
Amejiandaa, Jenny.

167
00:12:59,357 --> 00:13:00,525
Nenda, kijana.

168
00:13:02,401 --> 00:13:04,278
Unajua sheria za
jamii yetu, Spike.

169
00:13:05,154 --> 00:13:08,114
Ukiondoka, unaweza kurudi.
Lakini usiporudi...

170
00:13:08,115 --> 00:13:10,159
hakuna anayeruhusiwa kwenda kukutafuta.

171
00:13:10,743 --> 00:13:13,079
Hakuna uokozi. Hakuna ubaguzi.

172
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:16,374
Ni jambo
tulilojifunza kwa njia ngumu...

173
00:13:17,166 --> 00:13:19,585
Kwa sababu ya
watu wote tuliowapoteza zamani.

174
00:13:22,129 --> 00:13:25,967
Hivyo ukishafika tu bara,
utakuwa peke yako. Unanielewa?

175
00:13:27,635 --> 00:13:28,719
Ndiyo, Jenny.

176
00:13:32,515 --> 00:13:34,475
Umeona chochote asubuhi ya leo, Ant?

177
00:13:35,309 --> 00:13:36,768
Hakuna chochote.

178
00:13:36,769 --> 00:13:37,854
Shwari kabisa.

179
00:13:38,563 --> 00:13:39,729
Kuko sawa?

180
00:13:39,730 --> 00:13:41,023
Kuko sawa.

181
00:13:45,236 --> 00:13:46,279
Wafungulie.

182
00:13:50,867 --> 00:13:51,868
Kijana mzuri.

183
00:14:04,338 --> 00:14:06,757
Muwe waangalifu, vijana. Msikose maji kupwa.

184
00:14:08,968 --> 00:14:12,470
<i>Saba, sita, kumi na moja, tano...</i>

185
00:14:12,471 --> 00:14:14,264
<i>maili ishirini na tisa leo...</i>

186
00:14:14,265 --> 00:14:16,558
<i>Nne, kumi na moja, kumi na saba...</i>

187
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:18,018
<i>thelathini na mbili siku iliyotangulia...</i>

188
00:14:18,019 --> 00:14:21,730
<i>Buti, buti, buti...</i>

189
00:14:21,731 --> 00:14:23,773
<i>zikipanda na kushuka tena!</i>

190
00:14:23,774 --> 00:14:26,401
<i>Hakuna kuachishwa vitani!</i>

191
00:14:26,402 --> 00:14:27,903
Haya, Spike, hiki ni nini?

192
00:14:27,904 --> 00:14:30,655
 - Ni njia ya kuvukia. - Tueleze kuihusu.

193
00:14:30,656 --> 00:14:32,824
Ni njia pekee ya kuelekea bara.

194
00:14:32,825 --> 00:14:35,119
Lakini tunaweza kufika hapa wakati wa maji kupwa tu.

195
00:14:36,078 --> 00:14:38,413
Wakati wa maji kujaa, bahari huifunika.

196
00:14:38,414 --> 00:14:40,374
<i>Je, tunaweza kuogelea wakati wa maji kujaa?</i>

197
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:42,834
<i>Hapana. Bahari ina mkondo.</i>

198
00:14:42,835 --> 00:14:46,713
Itatusukuma kupita kisiwa na kutuvuta baharini...

199
00:14:46,714 --> 00:14:48,006
na tutazama.

200
00:14:48,007 --> 00:14:50,717
<i>Usitazame, usitazame, usitazame...</i>

201
00:14:50,718 --> 00:14:52,969
<i>usitazame kilicho mbele yako...</i>

202
00:14:52,970 --> 00:14:56,348
<i>Buti, buti, buti, buti...</i>

203
00:14:56,349 --> 00:14:58,141
<i>zikipanda na kushuka tena...</i>

204
00:14:58,142 --> 00:15:01,770
<i>Wanaume, wanaume, wanaume, wanaume...</i>

205
00:15:01,771 --> 00:15:03,230
<i>wanaume hupagawa kwa kuzitazama...</i>

206
00:15:03,231 --> 00:15:05,316
Tutakuwa na saa nne kabla ya maji kujaa.

207
00:15:06,984 --> 00:15:07,985
Je, tunafanya hili?

208
00:15:09,070 --> 00:15:11,531
 - Hatuwezi kurudi sasa, Baba. - Kwa nini?

209
00:15:12,156 --> 00:15:13,533
Kila mtu atadhani mimi ni dhaifu.

210
00:15:14,825 --> 00:15:15,825
Ndiyo, watafanya hivyo.

211
00:15:15,826 --> 00:15:17,370
Hatuwezi kuruhusu hilo, au siyo?

212
00:15:17,954 --> 00:15:19,371
Haya basi, twende.

213
00:15:19,372 --> 00:15:21,916
<i>Hesabu, hesabu, hesabu,</i>

214
00:15:22,291 --> 00:15:24,459
<i>hesabu risasi kwenye mishipi.</i>

215
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:27,838
<i>Macho yako yakifumba...</i>

216
00:15:27,839 --> 00:15:29,422
<i>watakuvamia!</i>

217
00:15:29,423 --> 00:15:32,592
<i>Buti, buti, buti, buti...</i>

218
00:15:32,593 --> 00:15:34,761
<i>zikipanda na kushuka tena...</i>

219
00:15:34,762 --> 00:15:37,640
<i>Hakuna kustaafu vitani!</i>

220
00:15:38,224 --> 00:15:39,976
Hapa ndipo tunapopata mafuta yote.

221
00:15:41,394 --> 00:15:43,103
Utakuja kufanya kazi hapa siku moja.

222
00:15:43,104 --> 00:15:46,398
<i>Sio mbaya sana mchana...</i>

223
00:15:46,399 --> 00:15:47,524
<i>kwa sababu ya wenzako...</i>

224
00:15:47,525 --> 00:15:50,735
<i>Lakini usiku huleta misururu mirefu...</i>

225
00:15:50,736 --> 00:15:52,362
<i>ya mamilioni elfu arobaini</i>

226
00:15:52,363 --> 00:15:55,615
<i>Buti, buti, buti, buti...</i>

227
00:15:55,616 --> 00:15:56,908
<i>zikipanda na kushuka tena.</i>

228
00:15:56,909 --> 00:15:58,327
Ni kubwa sana.

229
00:16:00,163 --> 00:16:01,329
Tukiendelea kutembea...

230
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:03,457
tungeweza kufika mahali ambapo huwezi kuona bahari?

231
00:16:04,667 --> 00:16:05,750
Ndiyo haswa.

232
00:16:05,751 --> 00:16:08,128
Utatembea kwa siku au wiki bila kuona pwani.

233
00:16:08,129 --> 00:16:10,339
Hakuna kitu huko nje, Spikey.

234
00:16:10,923 --> 00:16:12,591
Hakuna mahali pa kuelekea.

235
00:16:12,592 --> 00:16:14,092
Kuna vijiji vingine.

236
00:16:14,093 --> 00:16:16,178
Ndiyo, lakini hakuna kilicho na kitu ambacho hatuna.

237
00:16:16,179 --> 00:16:17,971
Na tunakaa mbali na miji na vijiji.

238
00:16:17,972 --> 00:16:20,348
<i>Nimetembea...</i>

239
00:16:20,349 --> 00:16:23,059
<i>- wiki sita motoni na nathibitisha... -</i> Haya basi.

240
00:16:23,060 --> 00:16:25,604
<i>Sio moto...</i>

241
00:16:25,605 --> 00:16:27,355
<i>mashetani, giza, au chochote...</i>

242
00:16:27,356 --> 00:16:31,026
<i>ila mabuti, mabuti, mabuti, mabuti...</i>

243
00:16:31,027 --> 00:16:33,029
<i>yakipanda na kushuka tena.</i>

244
00:16:38,868 --> 00:16:41,328
<i>Jaribu, jaribu, jaribu...</i>

245
00:16:41,329 --> 00:16:43,914
<i>jaribu kufikiria kitu kingine</i>

246
00:16:43,915 --> 00:16:46,082
<i>Ee Mungu wangu...</i>

247
00:16:46,083 --> 00:16:48,752
<i>niepushe nisiwe kichaa!</i>

248
00:16:48,753 --> 00:16:52,255
<i>Mabuti, mabuti, mabuti, mabuti...</i>

249
00:16:52,256 --> 00:16:54,049
<i>yakipanda na kushuka tena!</i>

250
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:57,720
<i>Hakuna mapumziko vitani!</i>

251
00:17:12,150 --> 00:17:14,153
Pale, tazama, tazama, tazama.

252
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:17,031
Polepole-pole.

253
00:17:18,658 --> 00:17:19,659
Si haraka.

254
00:17:21,159 --> 00:17:22,745
Haimaanishi kwamba si hatari.

255
00:17:23,871 --> 00:17:25,581
Na ikiwa mmoja anaonekana...

256
00:17:26,207 --> 00:17:27,958
pengine kuna wengine zaidi mitini.

257
00:17:31,629 --> 00:17:33,338
Upinde wako...

258
00:17:33,339 --> 00:17:35,091
hauna nguvu ya kutosha kwa ajili ya kifua.

259
00:17:35,675 --> 00:17:37,885
Unahitaji kukilenga shingoni kabisa.

260
00:17:39,428 --> 00:17:40,429
Sawa, Baba.

261
00:17:45,518 --> 00:17:46,519
Unaogopa?

262
00:17:47,812 --> 00:17:48,813
Kidogo tu. samples 

263
00:17:51,482 --> 00:17:53,818
- Na wewe? - Hapana. Niko sawa.

264
00:17:57,363 --> 00:17:58,530
Unapenda umbali huu?

265
00:17:58,531 --> 00:17:59,824
Nadhani hivyo.

266
00:18:00,408 --> 00:18:01,617
Twende tukapate mnyama wako wa kwanza.

267
00:18:20,303 --> 00:18:21,637
Muweke kwenye shabaha yako.

268
00:18:29,687 --> 00:18:31,022
Kadiria upepo.

269
00:18:33,441 --> 00:18:34,567
Haya.

270
00:18:35,234 --> 00:18:36,235
Ni wako.

271
00:18:37,278 --> 00:18:39,362
Kila kitakachotoka baada yake ni changu.

272
00:18:39,363 --> 00:18:40,740
Tuma ukiwa tayari.

273
00:18:44,577 --> 00:18:45,828
Tuma.

274
00:19:20,655 --> 00:19:21,697
Baba!

275
00:19:25,952 --> 00:19:27,620
<i>- Ingia humu!\n- Hey!</i>

276
00:19:30,331 --> 00:19:32,124
Uuaji bora, Spike.

277
00:19:33,125 --> 00:19:34,126
Unajihisi vizuri?

278
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:36,587
 - Ndiyo, nadhani hivyo.\n- Naam, unapaswa.

279
00:19:37,755 --> 00:19:38,840
Ninajivunia wewe.

280
00:19:39,882 --> 00:19:41,092
Haya, inabidi tuondoke.

281
00:19:41,759 --> 00:19:44,262
Kupiga kelele kungekuwa kumewatahadharisha\nwaambukizwa wengine katika eneo hili.

282
00:19:45,012 --> 00:19:46,472
Endelea. Tuendelee mbele.

283
00:20:41,485 --> 00:20:42,695
Ni wa ajabu sana.

284
00:20:43,905 --> 00:20:44,989
Ni wazuri.

285
00:20:49,952 --> 00:20:50,953
Hapa.

286
00:20:52,246 --> 00:20:53,289
Angalia hii.

287
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:01,881
Kijana mzuri.

288
00:21:25,530 --> 00:21:26,531
Laana.

289
00:21:33,704 --> 00:21:36,331
Daima inafaa kutazama huku na kule\nkwa ajili ya kitu chenye manufaa.

290
00:21:36,332 --> 00:21:40,753
Watu watakuwa wamepekua mahali hapa\nmara mia moja, lakini huwezi jua.

291
00:21:51,848 --> 00:21:52,849
Jamani.

292
00:22:00,857 --> 00:22:02,024
Je, hivi vina manufaa?

293
00:22:02,984 --> 00:22:04,693
Hapana. Ninavyo vingi hivyo.

294
00:22:04,694 --> 00:22:05,945
Lakini hiki kinafaa.

295
00:22:06,988 --> 00:22:07,989
Ni nini?

296
00:22:09,407 --> 00:22:10,448
Frisbee.

297
00:22:10,449 --> 00:22:12,200
Hujawahi kuona frisbee hapo awali?

298
00:22:12,201 --> 00:22:14,619
Ah, ni nzuri sana.

299
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:15,955
Utaipenda.

300
00:22:43,691 --> 00:22:44,859
Njoo hapa, mwanangu.

301
00:22:55,995 --> 00:22:57,455
Usitazame pembeni, Spike.

302
00:22:58,164 --> 00:22:59,247
- Baba, tafadhali.
- Spike!

303
00:22:59,248 --> 00:23:00,708
Fanya ninavyokuambia.

304
00:23:04,879 --> 00:23:06,672
Kuna funzo hapa kwa ajili yako.

305
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:27,527
Nini kilimpata?

306
00:23:28,819 --> 00:23:31,280
Inaonekana alifungwa
na kuachwa kwa walioambukizwa.

307
00:23:32,448 --> 00:23:33,741
Na sasa ameambukizwa.

308
00:23:34,575 --> 00:23:35,618
Ameambukizwa?

309
00:23:39,622 --> 00:23:40,790
Ndiyo.

310
00:23:41,457 --> 00:23:44,752
Kwa nini mtu afanye hivyo?
Labda ni adhabu.

311
00:23:47,630 --> 00:23:48,756
Labda ni onyo.

312
00:23:51,425 --> 00:23:53,469
Kuna watu wa ajabu huko bara.

313
00:23:54,887 --> 00:23:55,972
Wanazurura.

314
00:23:57,014 --> 00:23:58,891
Ndio maana nyumba yetu ni ya thamani sana.

315
00:24:01,978 --> 00:24:03,020
Hilo ndilo funzo?

316
00:24:03,729 --> 00:24:04,730
Hapana.

317
00:24:05,982 --> 00:24:07,024
Kiue.

318
00:24:10,736 --> 00:24:13,030
Kadiri unavyozidi kuua, ndivyo inavyokuwa rahisi.

319
00:24:16,284 --> 00:24:17,994
Usijisikie vibaya kwa hilo.

320
00:24:18,494 --> 00:24:20,288
Maambukizi yanawaondolea ufahamu.

321
00:24:22,123 --> 00:24:24,000
Hakina akili, hakina roho.

322
00:24:33,092 --> 00:24:34,177
Spike.

323
00:24:35,553 --> 00:24:36,637
Kiue hicho kitu kilicholaaniwa.

324
00:24:38,431 --> 00:24:39,432
Kiue!

325
00:24:40,641 --> 00:24:42,560
Unasubiri nini, Spike?

326
00:24:43,269 --> 00:24:44,270
Sasa, mwanangu!

327
00:24:45,313 --> 00:24:46,480
Spike, kimalize!

328
00:24:47,648 --> 00:24:50,109
Kwa ajili ya Kristo, Spike, kiue bwana!

329
00:24:59,202 --> 00:25:00,203
Kijana mzuri.

330
00:25:14,926 --> 00:25:18,095
<i>Kaa nami</i>

331
00:25:18,721 --> 00:25:23,976
<i>Giza la jioni linaingia haraka</i>

332
00:25:25,186 --> 00:25:29,856
<i>Giza linazidi kuwa nene</i>

333
00:25:29,857 --> 00:25:33,861
<i>Bwana, kaa nami</i>

334
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:38,698
<i>Uko wapi uchungu wa mauti?</i>

335
00:25:38,699 --> 00:25:42,954
 - Kichwa. Moyo. Vuta...\n<i>- Liko wapi, kaburi, ushindi wako?</i>

336
00:25:45,122 --> 00:25:46,748
<i>Bado nashinda</i>

337
00:25:46,749 --> 00:25:47,834
Achilia.

338
00:25:49,001 --> 00:25:51,671
<i>Ukikaa nami...</i>

339
00:26:21,701 --> 00:26:23,578
Kuna windo lingine hapa tukiwa na bahati.

340
00:26:24,412 --> 00:26:25,496
Haya.

341
00:26:37,717 --> 00:26:38,968
Hawa hawakuwa wale wa polepole.

342
00:26:40,428 --> 00:26:42,138
Hawa walikuwa wale wenye kasi, Spikey.

343
00:26:46,642 --> 00:26:47,643
Unasikia harufu hiyo?

344
00:26:48,436 --> 00:26:49,437
Ni matumbo.

345
00:26:52,023 --> 00:26:53,107
Inashangaza kuwa ninaipenda.

346
00:27:06,871 --> 00:27:07,872
Baba.

347
00:27:09,582 --> 00:27:10,791
Baba.

348
00:27:37,818 --> 00:27:38,819
Nini?

349
00:27:40,988 --> 00:27:42,281
Alpha ndiye aliyefanya hivi.

350
00:27:45,409 --> 00:27:46,993
Njia hii, Spike. Haya.

351
00:27:46,994 --> 00:27:48,079
Spike! Changamka!

352
00:27:51,499 --> 00:27:52,500
Tunarudi?

353
00:27:53,876 --> 00:27:56,254
Ndiyo. Umepata mawindo yako,\nhicho ndicho tulichokuja kutafuta.

354
00:27:57,797 --> 00:27:59,089
Je, haitaonekana kama tuliondoka mapema?

355
00:27:59,090 --> 00:28:01,676
Usiongee, Spikey.\nKaa macho tu.

356
00:28:06,305 --> 00:28:07,306
Kuko shwari.

357
00:28:07,807 --> 00:28:08,850
Twende.

358
00:28:23,739 --> 00:28:26,617
Tulia kabisa.

359
00:28:47,138 --> 00:28:48,139
Alpha.

360
00:28:48,890 --> 00:28:49,891
Pumbavu.

361
00:28:50,516 --> 00:28:51,808
Rudini kwenye miti.

362
00:28:51,809 --> 00:28:53,560
Rudi nyuma, twendeni.

363
00:28:53,561 --> 00:28:54,729
Baba!

364
00:29:09,452 --> 00:29:10,703
Twendeni!

365
00:29:16,501 --> 00:29:17,585
Sogea, sogea.

366
00:29:18,544 --> 00:29:20,254
Endelea kusogea. Twendeni, twendeni!

367
00:29:23,007 --> 00:29:24,967
Hapa, ulinzi. Tuliza pumzi.

368
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:28,137
- Nitamchukua wa kwanza, wewe chukua wa pili.\n- Sawa.

369
00:29:29,180 --> 00:29:30,181
Punguza upumuaji wako.

370
00:29:30,848 --> 00:29:31,849
Punguza kasi.

371
00:29:35,102 --> 00:29:36,103
Laana!

372
00:29:42,735 --> 00:29:44,986
Nenda! Sogea, sogea, sogea!

373
00:29:44,987 --> 00:29:46,155
Nenda tu!

374
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:48,741
Kumanina!

375
00:29:51,077 --> 00:29:53,454
Haya, zoezi la watu wawili. Ulinzi!

376
00:29:59,752 --> 00:30:01,504
Haya. Piga risasi!

377
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:05,466
Kichwa na moyo. Kichwa na moyo, Spike.

378
00:30:15,184 --> 00:30:16,185
Ingia humo.

379
00:30:17,228 --> 00:30:18,229
Panda juu!

380
00:30:24,735 --> 00:30:26,779
- Endelea, mwanangu!\n- Haya, Baba! Wapi?

381
00:30:29,198 --> 00:30:30,199
Laana.

382
00:30:32,243 --> 00:30:34,412
- Ba, nini...?\n- Darini! Kagulia darini!

383
00:30:39,625 --> 00:30:40,626
Njoo hapa.

384
00:30:44,172 --> 00:30:45,173
Endelea.

385
00:30:45,715 --> 00:30:47,048
Siwezi kurudi juu.

386
00:30:47,049 --> 00:30:49,468
- Oh, kumanina.\n- Baba! Baba!

387
00:30:57,393 --> 00:30:58,519
Sukuma!

388
00:31:03,649 --> 00:31:04,650
Oh, kumanina.

389
00:31:11,991 --> 00:31:13,534
Kumanina kabisa.

390
00:31:55,743 --> 00:31:57,203
Angalieni nyuma yenu, vijana.

391
00:31:57,745 --> 00:31:58,871
Napisheni!

392
00:32:00,081 --> 00:32:01,207
Wakati wa chai.

393
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:03,793
Wakati wa chai. Kazi nzuri leo.

394
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:05,628
Safi sana.

395
00:32:06,587 --> 00:32:08,464
Haya, chapuchapu kabla kiza hakijaingia.

396
00:32:25,147 --> 00:32:26,357
Linangoja.

397
00:32:27,984 --> 00:32:29,652
Hao Alphas si kama wengine.

398
00:32:30,361 --> 00:32:32,780
Si wakubwa tu. Wana akili zaidi.

399
00:32:33,990 --> 00:32:35,199
Tutafanya nini?

400
00:32:36,075 --> 00:32:37,410
Basi, hatupigani nalo.

401
00:32:39,871 --> 00:32:41,330
Sina mishale iliyobaki.

402
00:32:43,416 --> 00:32:44,583
Na hata hivyo...

403
00:32:44,584 --> 00:32:47,670
Nimeona inahitaji mapigo mengi kuliangusha moja ya vitu hivyo.

404
00:32:49,255 --> 00:32:51,299
Hivyo, tutasubiri pia.

405
00:32:54,302 --> 00:32:56,012
Samahani sana, Baba.

406
00:32:56,596 --> 00:32:58,181
Nini? Kuhusu nini?

407
00:32:59,265 --> 00:33:00,850
Hii yote ni kosa langu.

408
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:03,351
- Sikuweza kupiga chochote. - Unazungumza nini?

409
00:33:03,352 --> 00:33:06,313
Nilijaribu lakini niliogopa sana. Na niliendelea kukosa.

410
00:33:06,314 --> 00:33:08,398
Unazungumza nini? Hili si kosa lako.

411
00:33:08,399 --> 00:33:10,026
Na uliendelea kupiga.

412
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:13,820
Nimeona watu wazima wasioweza hata kuweka mshale kwenye upinde, wakitetemeka kupita kiasi.

413
00:33:13,821 --> 00:33:15,948
Sio wewe. Haya, haya, haya...

414
00:33:16,949 --> 00:33:19,160
Spike, ulifanya vizuri.

415
00:33:20,745 --> 00:33:21,913
Kiukweli.

416
00:33:27,502 --> 00:33:28,920
Tutapitwa na wakati wa maji kupwa.

417
00:33:29,545 --> 00:33:31,046
- Ndiyo. Ndiyo. - Au sivyo?

418
00:33:31,047 --> 00:33:32,340
Kutakuwa na nyingine.

419
00:33:43,726 --> 00:33:45,520
Hebu, angalia kule baharini.

420
00:33:47,146 --> 00:33:48,147
Hapa.

421
00:33:51,526 --> 00:33:52,527
Hapo tu.

422
00:33:53,945 --> 00:33:55,530
Doria ya karantini.

423
00:33:56,822 --> 00:33:57,907
Huenda ni Kifaransa.

424
00:34:17,343 --> 00:34:18,344
Baba...

425
00:34:19,512 --> 00:34:20,512
Ni nini hicho?

426
00:34:28,354 --> 00:34:29,396
Moto.

427
00:34:30,106 --> 00:34:31,524
Kuna kitu kinaungua?

428
00:34:32,191 --> 00:34:33,191
Ndiyo.

429
00:34:33,901 --> 00:34:34,902
Kitu fulani.

430
00:34:36,653 --> 00:34:38,114
Ni kijiji kingine?

431
00:34:39,615 --> 00:34:40,615
Hapana.

432
00:34:42,410 --> 00:34:43,411
Sasa ni nini?

433
00:34:44,162 --> 00:34:46,289
Sijui. Sijawahi kufika huko.

434
00:34:47,999 --> 00:34:49,082
Je, huwa unawaka kila wakati?

435
00:34:49,083 --> 00:34:51,001
Nimesema tu sijawahi kufika huko, Spike.

436
00:35:23,367 --> 00:35:24,535
Spike.

437
00:35:27,371 --> 00:35:28,413
Spike.

438
00:35:28,414 --> 00:35:29,499
Huyo hapo.

439
00:35:29,957 --> 00:35:31,292
Spike, ninazama.

440
00:35:53,648 --> 00:35:55,191
Toka! Lazima tutoke!

441
00:35:56,359 --> 00:35:57,735
Haki ya Mungu.

442
00:35:58,528 --> 00:35:59,987
Amka! Amka, Spike!

443
00:36:01,113 --> 00:36:03,115
- Inama chini. - Amka, lazima tuondoke!

444
00:36:09,789 --> 00:36:11,624
Ni sawa, mwanangu. Ni sawa.

445
00:36:12,458 --> 00:36:13,459
Pumbavu!

446
00:36:19,382 --> 00:36:21,259
- Nini kimetokea? - Jengo la zamani.

447
00:36:22,301 --> 00:36:24,678
Sijui. Bomba la moshi limeharibika vibaya sana.

448
00:36:24,679 --> 00:36:26,346
Kelele zitawaleta.

449
00:36:26,347 --> 00:36:27,431
Lazima tuondoke.

450
00:36:28,391 --> 00:36:30,601
- Je, ni maji kupwa? - Yatakuwa yamepungua vya kutosha.

451
00:36:31,853 --> 00:36:33,478
Tunasogea haraka lakini kimya.

452
00:36:33,479 --> 00:36:37,899
Ukimuona Alpha, kimbia moja kwa moja kuelekea njia ya kivuko na uivuke. Sawa?

453
00:36:37,900 --> 00:36:40,402
Usisimame kwa lolote! Nenda!out 

454
00:36:40,403 --> 00:36:42,572
- Utakuwa wapi? - Nyuma yako kabisa.

455
00:36:59,922 --> 00:37:01,299
Hakuna dalili ya Alpha.

456
00:37:02,216 --> 00:37:03,550
Maji bado yamejaa.

457
00:37:03,551 --> 00:37:04,802
Ni sasa hivi tu.

458
00:37:05,344 --> 00:37:06,679
Maji yatakuwa mafupi. Lakini tunaweza kuvuka.

459
00:37:19,108 --> 00:37:21,277
Kina cha muundi. Tuko sawa. Haya.

460
00:37:22,361 --> 00:37:23,487
Vua mabuti yako.

461
00:37:24,363 --> 00:37:26,282
Sawa. Linganisha malango.

462
00:37:27,742 --> 00:37:28,743
Hiyo ndiyo njia yetu.

463
00:37:30,244 --> 00:37:32,287
Ni sawa. Pumua tu.

464
00:37:32,288 --> 00:37:34,040
Hapa. Twende.

465
00:37:34,957 --> 00:37:35,958
Wewe tangulia.

466
00:37:41,255 --> 00:37:42,298
Nenda, mwanangu.

467
00:38:03,986 --> 00:38:06,948
Vipi kuhusu siku ile, Spike, eh?

468
00:38:07,615 --> 00:38:09,199
Mara ya kwanza nchi kavu.

469
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:12,495
Uuaji wa kwanza. Mgongano wa kwanza na walioambukizwa.

470
00:38:13,287 --> 00:38:14,664
Nilimwona Alpha!

471
00:38:15,665 --> 00:38:16,666
Na tukakosa wakati wa maji kupwa.

472
00:38:17,792 --> 00:38:19,877
Nina mengi ya kumwambia Mama tutakaporudi.

473
00:38:38,563 --> 00:38:39,564
Baba.

474
00:38:41,274 --> 00:38:42,650
Kimbia, Spike!

475
00:38:43,985 --> 00:38:45,236
Kimbia!

476
00:38:46,195 --> 00:38:48,281
Nenda! Nenda, endelea!

477
00:38:54,871 --> 00:38:55,872
Endelea kusogea!out 

478
00:38:58,416 --> 00:39:00,041
- Ee Mungu! Inuka! - Baba, siwezi!out 

479
00:39:00,042 --> 00:39:02,670
- Siwezi! - Spike! Inuka, sasa hivi!

480
00:39:04,130 --> 00:39:06,382
Spike, nenda! Nenda, nenda, Spike!

481
00:39:07,383 --> 00:39:08,384
Nenda upesi!

482
00:39:13,764 --> 00:39:16,058
 - Siwezi!
- Ndiyo, unaweza!

483
00:39:21,355 --> 00:39:22,523
Laana!

484
00:39:25,443 --> 00:39:27,320
Inakuja!

485
00:39:28,196 --> 00:39:29,614
Fungua!

486
00:39:31,699 --> 00:39:35,620
Saidia! Jenny! Jenny!

487
00:39:36,454 --> 00:39:38,705
Amka, amka! Inuka, inuka, inuka!

488
00:39:38,706 --> 00:39:41,459
Inakuja!

489
00:39:42,251 --> 00:39:43,627
 - Amkeni, amkeni, vijana.
- Ant, ni nani huyo?

490
00:39:43,628 --> 00:39:45,045
 - Kila mtu amke! Macho mbele!
- Jipangeni, vijana! Kaeni tayari!

491
00:39:45,046 --> 00:39:47,173
 - Macho mbele, macho mbele!
- Inakuja!

492
00:39:53,721 --> 00:39:55,555
Alpha!

493
00:39:55,556 --> 00:39:58,600
Fungua! Fungua sasa hivi!

494
00:39:58,601 --> 00:40:00,685
Alpha! Alpha!

495
00:40:00,686 --> 00:40:02,604
Alpha, washa hiyo taa upesi!

496
00:40:02,605 --> 00:40:04,272
 - Endelea kumulika taa kwake!
- Fyatueni!

497
00:40:04,273 --> 00:40:05,441
Lala chini!

498
00:40:13,908 --> 00:40:15,992
Nenda, nenda, nenda, Spike!

499
00:40:15,993 --> 00:40:18,078
 - Nenda, nenda.
- Endelea kumulika hiyo taa kwake.

500
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:20,705
Lipakie, lipakie, lipakie!

501
00:40:20,706 --> 00:40:22,917
Laana. Hii ndiyo sasa, Spike.

502
00:40:24,001 --> 00:40:25,294
Vuta pumzi!

503
00:40:29,465 --> 00:40:30,466
Laana!

504
00:40:33,052 --> 00:40:35,804
<i>Laiti, vijana wangu, mngetuona tukienda</i>

505
00:40:35,805 --> 00:40:38,014
<i>- Tukipita watu kando ya barabara</i>
- Fungua!

506
00:40:38,015 --> 00:40:39,975
<i>Wakati walikuwa wamesimama
Vijana wote...</i>

507
00:40:39,976 --> 00:40:43,144
<i>- na wasichana wote huko wenye nyuso za tabasamu</i>
- Jenny! Fungua hilo lango sasa hivi!

508
00:40:43,145 --> 00:40:44,896
<i>- Tukienda kwenye Barabara ya Scotswood</i>
- Subiri.

509
00:40:44,897 --> 00:40:46,774
Hapana, fungua mara moja!

510
00:40:48,317 --> 00:40:49,317
Kha!

511
00:40:49,318 --> 00:40:50,527
- Ngoja.
- Hapana.

512
00:40:50,528 --> 00:40:51,987
- Laana, Jenny!
- Tafadhali, tafadhali.

513
00:40:51,988 --> 00:40:53,322
- Tuko safi kabisa.
- Ngoja.

514
00:40:54,115 --> 00:40:56,784
- Angalia macho yangu, tuko safi.
- Ngoja.

515
00:40:59,328 --> 00:41:00,620
Mwangalie.

516
00:41:00,621 --> 00:41:01,913
- Angalia macho yake!
- Jenny.

517
00:41:01,914 --> 00:41:04,125
- Hana maambukizi! Tuko safi!
- Jenny, tafadhali.

518
00:41:04,876 --> 00:41:06,459
Haya, fungua, waache waingie.

519
00:41:06,460 --> 00:41:07,836
Nendeni. Nendeni.

520
00:41:07,837 --> 00:41:11,674
<i>Kuona Mashindano ya Blaydon</i>

521
00:41:18,389 --> 00:41:22,350
Spike! Spike! Spike!

522
00:41:22,351 --> 00:41:23,768
Hey!

523
00:41:23,769 --> 00:41:26,646
Walikuwepo 25, yapata yadi 30.

524
00:41:26,647 --> 00:41:29,066
Nyasi ndefu. Upepo.

525
00:41:30,401 --> 00:41:32,195
Na ule mshale ulienda wapi?

526
00:41:33,362 --> 00:41:35,406
Moja kwa moja kwenye shingo yake!

527
00:41:39,702 --> 00:41:41,786
Yule mnono mpuuzi, anasimama...

528
00:41:41,787 --> 00:41:43,915
na kutoa moja ya zile kelele za kike...

529
00:41:45,458 --> 00:41:48,377
na kisha anaanguka kama
gunia la mavi.

530
00:41:50,922 --> 00:41:54,007
Kitu kilichofuata,
tukawa na walioambukizwa wanane...

531
00:41:54,008 --> 00:41:55,467
Baba, matusi.

532
00:41:55,468 --> 00:41:57,303
...wakikimbia moja kwa moja kwetu!

533
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:02,308
Nawaza, "Lahaula, ndiyo hiyo sasa."

534
00:42:03,392 --> 00:42:06,646
Benny Kende-Kubwa hapa
anapiga tu risasi.

535
00:42:08,022 --> 00:42:12,443
<i>Alisimama pale akicheka</i>

536
00:42:13,236 --> 00:42:14,986
- Hapana, niliendelea kuwakosa.
- Hamna, hukuwakosa.

537
00:42:14,987 --> 00:42:17,155
- Ni mnyenyekevu. Spike wetu mnyenyekevu.
<i>- Nilihisi kisu mkononi mwangu</i>

538
00:42:17,156 --> 00:42:18,949
<i>Na hakucheka tena</i>

539
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:20,409
Muuaji mkuu wa majitu!

540
00:42:22,495 --> 00:42:27,208
<i>Lo, lo, lo Delilah</i>

541
00:42:29,752 --> 00:42:34,673
<i>Kwa nini, kwa nini, kwa nini, Delilah?</i>

542
00:42:34,674 --> 00:42:36,300
Endelea. Haya, nenda.

543
00:42:37,301 --> 00:42:41,388
<i>Basi kabla hawajaja</i>

544
00:42:41,389 --> 00:42:44,474
<i>Kuvunja mlango</i>

545
00:42:44,475 --> 00:42:49,313
<i>Unisamehe, Delilah
Sikuweza kuvumilia zaidi</i>

546
00:42:51,607 --> 00:42:53,400
<i>Unisamehe, Delilah</i>

547
00:42:53,401 --> 00:42:57,487
<i>Sikuweza kuvumilia zaidi</i>

548
00:42:57,488 --> 00:42:58,739
Lazima niende.

549
00:43:18,801 --> 00:43:20,011
Huku ndani.

550
00:43:24,599 --> 00:43:25,600
Haya, Rosey.

551
00:43:26,684 --> 00:43:29,228
Nini... Unafanya nini...
Kwa nini unatuleta hapa?

552
00:43:35,443 --> 00:43:36,444
Oh, Rosey.

553
00:43:38,112 --> 00:43:39,113
Lahaula.

554
00:43:42,366 --> 00:43:44,660
Oh, Rosey.

555
00:44:22,698 --> 00:44:23,783
Spike.

556
00:44:24,367 --> 00:44:27,118
Sikutegemea kukuona
hadi baada ya usiku wa manane.

557
00:44:27,119 --> 00:44:28,537
Nimekuja tu kumwona mama.

558
00:44:28,538 --> 00:44:30,873
Alikuwaje? Je, yuko sawa?

559
00:44:31,833 --> 00:44:33,459
Yuko vizuri zaidi ya sawa.

560
00:44:34,752 --> 00:44:36,127
Tulikuwa tukizunguka huku na kule.

561
00:44:36,128 --> 00:44:37,879
Tulitembea hadi mashambani.

562
00:44:37,880 --> 00:44:40,758
Ana nguvu nyingi sana
wakati hali yake inapokuwa shwari.

563
00:44:41,843 --> 00:44:43,344
Lakini vipi kuhusu siku yako?

564
00:44:45,471 --> 00:44:46,888
Muhimu zaidi.

565
00:44:46,889 --> 00:44:48,932
Baba ameikuza ionekane
kama kitu ambacho si kweli. film- Kama nini?
- Kama mimi ni shujaa.

566
00:44:48,933 --> 00:44:51,476
Nadhani kwake wewe ni shujaa.

567
00:44:51,477 --> 00:44:53,729
Inahisi tu kama anadanganya.

568
00:44:55,022 --> 00:44:56,732
Hivyo nini kilitokea huko nje?

569
00:44:58,067 --> 00:45:00,194
Nilimpiga risasi mmoja wa wale wanene.

570
00:45:01,320 --> 00:45:02,989
I shot one of the fat ones.

571
00:45:03,781 --> 00:45:04,782
Kilikuwa hakisogei kabisa.

572
00:45:05,825 --> 00:45:07,994
Lakini halafu tulifukuzwa na baadhi ya wale wenye kasi...

573
00:45:09,036 --> 00:45:10,454
na sikuweza kupiga chochote.

574
00:45:12,248 --> 00:45:14,208
Halafu tukajificha tu mpaka kulipoingia giza.

575
00:45:16,419 --> 00:45:17,587
Nilikuwa nimeogopa tu.

576
00:45:18,838 --> 00:45:19,839
Nilihisi vibaya.

577
00:45:21,716 --> 00:45:23,508
Nilitaka kuwa nyumbani na mama yangu.

578
00:45:23,509 --> 00:45:25,636
Baba yako huenda alihisi vivyo hivyo pia.

579
00:45:30,266 --> 00:45:33,768
Ila nikuambie kitu, sijawahi kuona ardhi kubwa hivi.

580
00:45:33,769 --> 00:45:34,895
Ilikuwa kubwa sana.

581
00:45:34,896 --> 00:45:36,271
Uliona nini?

582
00:45:36,272 --> 00:45:38,065
Kweli, vilima...

583
00:45:38,691 --> 00:45:39,692
Misitu...

584
00:45:41,569 --> 00:45:42,737
Na moto.

585
00:45:44,655 --> 00:45:45,990
Moto?

586
00:45:49,702 --> 00:45:51,621
Nashangaa kama ulimuona mzee Kelson.

587
00:45:52,079 --> 00:45:53,998
Sikutegemea kama bado yu hai.

588
00:45:56,918 --> 00:45:58,002
Ilikuwa kusini magharibi?

589
00:46:00,630 --> 00:46:02,965
Kristo. Huyo atakuwa Kelson.

590
00:46:07,303 --> 00:46:08,345
Amini usiamini...

591
00:46:08,346 --> 00:46:10,556
alikuwa daktari wangu wa familia...

592
00:46:11,766 --> 00:46:13,266
takriban miaka 30 iliyopita. social.

593
00:46:13,267 --> 00:46:15,852
 - GP ni nini? - Daktari.

594
00:46:15,853 --> 00:46:17,687
 - Daktari? - Ndiyo.

595
00:46:17,688 --> 00:46:20,525
Alikuwa na kliniki yake nje kidogo ya Whitley Bay.

596
00:46:23,486 --> 00:46:25,530
Baba alisema kwamba hakujua moto ule ulikuwa wa nini.

597
00:46:26,864 --> 00:46:29,199
Na anasema madaktari wote wa kweli wamekufa.

598
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:31,410
Ndiyo maana hakuna anayejua kuna tatizo gani na Mama.

599
00:46:33,037 --> 00:46:35,163
Inahisiwa tu kama anadanganya kuhusu kila kitu.

600
00:46:35,164 --> 00:46:37,250
Hapana. Unajua nini?

601
00:46:40,253 --> 00:46:42,171
Pengine hakutaka kukuogopesha.

602
00:46:43,297 --> 00:46:44,549
Dkt Kelson ni...

603
00:46:47,176 --> 00:46:48,177
wa ajabu.

604
00:46:48,719 --> 00:46:49,762
Ni wa ajabu kwa namna gani?

605
00:46:52,849 --> 00:46:54,683
Kuna nini cha pekee kuhusu huo moto?

606
00:46:54,684 --> 00:46:57,311
Ikiwa baba yako hataki kuzungumzia hilo,
sidhani kama mimi napaswa.

607
00:47:00,773 --> 00:47:02,775
Kwa nini usirudi kwenye sherehe yako?

608
00:47:04,861 --> 00:47:06,194
Niko sawa hapa na mama yako.

609
00:47:06,195 --> 00:47:07,280
Hapana.

610
00:47:07,864 --> 00:47:08,865
Nenda wewe.

611
00:47:10,449 --> 00:47:11,701
Nitamtunza mimi sasa.

612
00:47:15,496 --> 00:47:16,497
Sawa.

613
00:47:23,171 --> 00:47:24,172
Nimekupata.

614
00:47:50,781 --> 00:47:52,074
Wote wanadanganya, Mama.

615
00:48:03,878 --> 00:48:05,755
Spike, utatuendea madukani?

616
00:48:07,089 --> 00:48:08,591
Nahitaji Nurofen.

617
00:48:11,928 --> 00:48:13,011
Nurofen?

618
00:48:13,012 --> 00:48:14,722
Ni kichwa changu. Ni...

619
00:48:20,269 --> 00:48:22,271
Usijali. Haijalishi.

620
00:48:23,314 --> 00:48:24,315
Habari!

621
00:48:24,941 --> 00:48:26,359
Tuko huku juu, mpenzi.

622
00:48:29,654 --> 00:48:31,780
Lo, hiyo ilikuwa sherehe kwelikweli.

623
00:48:31,781 --> 00:48:34,241
Vurugu tupu.

624
00:48:34,242 --> 00:48:35,450
Unaonekana...

625
00:48:35,451 --> 00:48:38,162
Unaonekana kama umevutwa
kwenye kichaka kinyumenyume.

626
00:48:38,746 --> 00:48:39,789
Labda ndivyo ilivyokuwa.

627
00:48:40,873 --> 00:48:43,124
Niliamka kwenye shamba la ngano.

628
00:48:43,125 --> 00:48:45,711
Na ulitowekea wapi, Spikey?

629
00:48:46,295 --> 00:48:49,423
Niliangalia huku na huku
na mgeni wa heshima alikuwa ametoweka.

630
00:48:50,424 --> 00:48:51,675
Nilirudi nyumbani tu.

631
00:48:51,676 --> 00:48:53,803
Hujambo, mwuaji-majitu.

632
00:49:12,697 --> 00:49:14,031
Nitapika kiamsha kinywa.

633
00:49:27,253 --> 00:49:28,337
Kuna nini, Spike?

634
00:49:28,921 --> 00:49:31,840
Mbona hukutuambia
kuna daktari angeweza kumwona Mama?

635
00:49:31,841 --> 00:49:33,176
Daktari?

636
00:49:34,802 --> 00:49:37,512
Hatuna daktari.
Hatujawa na daktari hapa tangu zamani.

637
00:49:37,513 --> 00:49:39,347
Dkt. Kelson, Baba.

638
00:49:39,348 --> 00:49:41,224
Ule moto. Bara.

639
00:49:41,225 --> 00:49:42,727
Umekuwa ukiongea na nani?

640
00:49:44,353 --> 00:49:45,354
Kwa hiyo yeye ni daktari.

641
00:49:45,938 --> 00:49:46,939
Alikuwa ni Sam?

642
00:49:47,690 --> 00:49:48,691
Mpumbavu mkubwa.

643
00:49:49,483 --> 00:49:50,902
Anakujaza mawazo kichwani.

644
00:49:53,029 --> 00:49:55,031
Yeye si daktari, Spike.

645
00:49:55,615 --> 00:49:57,742
Huenda aliwahi kuwa. Miaka mingi iliyopita.

646
00:49:58,910 --> 00:50:01,287
Lakini alishapoteza akili tangu zamani.

647
00:50:02,538 --> 00:50:03,581
Unamaanisha nini?

648
00:50:04,749 --> 00:50:06,459
Yeye ni daktari au la?

649
00:50:09,003 --> 00:50:10,463
Kabla hujazaliwa...

650
00:50:11,380 --> 00:50:12,590
tulikuwa tukitafuta chakula.

651
00:50:14,175 --> 00:50:16,259
Lakini ikawa vigumu zaidi, unajua,
hivyo ilibidi usafiri mbali zaidi.

652
00:50:16,260 --> 00:50:18,721
Na siku moja,
ikalipeleka kundi letu karibu na kwa akina Kelson.

653
00:50:20,139 --> 00:50:21,224
Sivyo?

654
00:50:22,016 --> 00:50:23,976
Ndiyo. Yadi 500 hivi...

655
00:50:24,852 --> 00:50:26,771
tulianza kusikia harufu ya kifo.

656
00:50:27,980 --> 00:50:29,898
Sasa elewa,
tulikuwa tumeizoea sana harufu hiyo.

657
00:50:29,899 --> 00:50:31,609
Zamani hizo, wafu walikuwa kila mahali.

658
00:50:32,735 --> 00:50:33,778
Lakini hii...

659
00:50:34,737 --> 00:50:36,113
hii ilikuwa tofauti kabisa.

660
00:50:37,907 --> 00:50:39,283
Uvundo huu ulikuwa kama...

661
00:50:41,077 --> 00:50:42,286
ilikuwa kama ukuta.

662
00:50:42,787 --> 00:50:43,955
Ungeweza kuigusa.

663
00:50:46,332 --> 00:50:48,626
<i>Nasi tukafika kilele cha kilima hiki...</i>

664
00:50:49,752 --> 00:50:50,920
<i>na tukatazama chini...</i>

665
00:50:54,006 --> 00:50:56,884
<i>Sijawahi kuona kitu kama hicho.</i>

666
00:50:59,595 --> 00:51:00,596
Maiti.

667
00:51:01,305 --> 00:51:02,473
Mamia.

668
00:51:06,519 --> 00:51:09,272
<i>Zimepangwa tu katika mistari.</i>

669
00:51:10,940 --> 00:51:13,234
Wanaume, wanawake, watoto.

670
00:51:14,485 --> 00:51:16,279
Na katikati, kulikuwa na moto huu.

671
00:51:18,364 --> 00:51:19,824
Akiwa amesimama kando yake, alikuwa Kelson.

672
00:51:21,701 --> 00:51:26,247
<i>Kwa kusudi lisiloeleweka,
alikuwa ameburuta miili yote pale.</i>

673
00:51:27,331 --> 00:51:31,293
Na sekunde chache baadaye, aligeuka
na kututazama moja kwa moja...

674
00:51:31,294 --> 00:51:32,711
<i>na akapungia mkono.</i>

675
00:51:32,712 --> 00:51:35,464
<i>Kikawaida tu, kama,
"Mambo. Mnataka kuja chini, vijana?"</i>

676
00:51:38,843 --> 00:51:40,720
Ndiyo. Tuligeuka na kukimbia.

677
00:51:41,596 --> 00:51:43,264
Na katika miaka 15...

678
00:51:44,223 --> 00:51:45,850
hakuna hata mmoja wetu aliyerudi.

679
00:51:48,394 --> 00:51:49,520
Kama nilivyosema.

680
00:51:51,230 --> 00:51:52,231
Kichaa.

681
00:51:56,027 --> 00:51:57,278
O, pumbavu.

682
00:52:01,157 --> 00:52:02,533
Unataka Mama afe?

683
00:52:04,327 --> 00:52:05,786
Bila shaka sitaki.

684
00:52:07,580 --> 00:52:10,082
Spike, ni swali la aina gani hilo?

685
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:12,376
Ana shida gani hasa?

686
00:52:17,590 --> 00:52:18,591
Sijui.

687
00:52:20,092 --> 00:52:21,219
Anakufa?

688
00:52:24,680 --> 00:52:25,681
Sijui.

689
00:52:27,517 --> 00:52:29,143
Nafikiri anakufa.

690
00:52:30,269 --> 00:52:31,395
Nawe pia unafikiri hivyo.

691
00:52:33,397 --> 00:52:34,439
Akifa...

692
00:52:34,440 --> 00:52:36,526
utakuwa na Rosey?

693
00:52:38,194 --> 00:52:39,486
Chunga mdomo wako.

694
00:52:39,487 --> 00:52:40,737
Davey wake angefikiria nini kuhusu hilo?

695
00:52:40,738 --> 00:52:42,949
Nimesema, chunga mdomo wako mchafu!

696
00:52:46,035 --> 00:52:47,077
Mwanangu...

697
00:52:47,078 --> 00:52:48,913
Jamie!

698
00:52:49,914 --> 00:52:50,915
Spike!

699
00:52:56,921 --> 00:52:59,673
Inadunda, Spike. Inadunda.

700
00:52:59,674 --> 00:53:01,342
Najua, Mama. Samahani.

701
00:53:06,347 --> 00:53:08,599
Unahitaji maji, mpenzi?
Nitaenda kukuletea.

702
00:53:10,309 --> 00:53:12,270
Ondokeni kabisa mbali nasi.

703
00:53:13,187 --> 00:53:14,188
"Mbali nasi"?

704
00:53:19,443 --> 00:53:20,528
Umetusikia.

705
00:53:40,131 --> 00:53:41,424
Nenda zako tu, Baba.

706
00:54:25,968 --> 00:54:26,969
Kuna moto!

707
00:54:28,679 --> 00:54:29,888
Kuna... Kimbia! text-align:center; 

708
00:54:29,889 --> 00:54:32,057
- Moshi mwingi, tazama.
- Ant, Mark! text-align:center; 

709
00:54:32,058 --> 00:54:33,975
- Kuna moto!
- Nenda, nenda, haya nenda! Nenda!

710
00:54:33,976 --> 00:54:35,144
Kuna moto kwenye ghala kuu! text-align:center; 

711
00:54:35,645 --> 00:54:37,855
- Lazima uende!
- Siwezi kuacha lango, Spike.

712
00:54:39,649 --> 00:54:40,649
Lazima.

713
00:54:40,650 --> 00:54:42,526
Ndio maana walinituma.

714
00:54:42,527 --> 00:54:45,070
Nitakuwa kwenye kingora.
Lakini lazima uende sasa.

715
00:54:45,071 --> 00:54:47,030
Walisema wanahitaji kila mtu! text-align:center; 

716
00:54:47,031 --> 00:54:48,907
- Nenda!
- Laana kabisa. text-align:center; 

717
00:54:48,908 --> 00:54:50,617
- Haraka.
- Shenzi... text-align:center; 

718
00:54:50,618 --> 00:54:52,661
- Nenda.
- Kazia macho upeo wa macho.

719
00:54:52,662 --> 00:54:54,497
Na uendelee kupiga kingora!

720
00:54:55,122 --> 00:54:56,540
Naenda kuchota maji zaidi!

721
00:54:56,541 --> 00:54:58,376
Chota maji zaidi!

722
00:55:01,712 --> 00:55:02,922
Moto!

723
00:55:04,882 --> 00:55:06,424
Chota maji zaidi. Nenda!

724
00:55:06,425 --> 00:55:07,593
Moto!

725
00:55:13,224 --> 00:55:15,642
Haya, Mama. Twende.

726
00:55:15,643 --> 00:55:18,353
 - Leta maji! Maji!
- Chota maji zaidi baharini!

727
00:55:18,354 --> 00:55:21,107
 - Tunaenda wapi?
- Pwani.

728
00:55:21,858 --> 00:55:23,358
Na mashambani.

729
00:55:23,359 --> 00:55:24,527
 - Tunaenda pwani?
- Ndiyo.

730
00:55:57,101 --> 00:55:58,436
Huku ni bara.

731
00:56:00,229 --> 00:56:01,230
Ndiyo.

732
00:56:01,856 --> 00:56:02,857
Lakini hatuwezi...

733
00:56:03,983 --> 00:56:05,735
Hatuwezi kuwa bara.

734
00:56:06,569 --> 00:56:08,111
Ni hatari sana. Ni...

735
00:56:08,112 --> 00:56:09,738
 - Ni sawa, Mama.
- Hapana.

736
00:56:09,739 --> 00:56:12,032
 - Najua jinsi ya kutuweka salama.
- Hapana, hapana, hapana, hii si sawa.

737
00:56:12,033 --> 00:56:13,367
Hii si sawa. Yuko wapi...?

738
00:56:14,493 --> 00:56:15,703
Jamie?

739
00:56:16,496 --> 00:56:17,497
Yuko wapi...

740
00:56:19,499 --> 00:56:20,957
Yuko wapi Baba?

741
00:56:20,958 --> 00:56:23,210
 - Baba hayupo hapa.
- Basi inabidi...

742
00:56:23,211 --> 00:56:26,046
Basi inabidi turudi sasa hivi. Nyumbani.
Inabidi tukimbie, ama tuta...

743
00:56:26,047 --> 00:56:27,131
Mama...

744
00:56:28,049 --> 00:56:30,592
Hatuwezi kurudi. Maji yamejaa.

745
00:56:30,593 --> 00:56:32,929
Ee Mungu.

746
00:56:34,931 --> 00:56:37,307
 - Tunaenda kumwona daktari.
- Nini? Daktari?

747
00:56:37,308 --> 00:56:39,435
 - Daktari halisi. Wa tangu zamani.
- Hapana.

748
00:56:40,478 --> 00:56:42,146
Kuna kitu hakiko sawa nawe, Mama.

749
00:56:45,274 --> 00:56:46,859
Daktari atakutibu upone.

750
00:56:50,655 --> 00:56:51,656
Sawa?

751
00:56:53,199 --> 00:56:54,200
Sawa.

752
00:57:45,918 --> 00:57:46,919
Sawa, Mama.

753
00:57:47,753 --> 00:57:49,088
Tutapumzika hapa kwa usiku huu.

754
00:57:51,591 --> 00:57:52,800
Tutakaa pale.

755
00:58:12,195 --> 00:58:13,321
Je, baba yako ni mcheshi? color? 

756
00:58:18,910 --> 00:58:20,161
- Baba?
- Ndiyo.

757
00:58:20,786 --> 00:58:22,371
Mcheshi kwako. Mtu wa utani.

758
00:58:26,167 --> 00:58:27,627
Babu yako alikuwa mcheshi sana.

759
00:58:29,170 --> 00:58:30,796
Hutaamini kwa kiasi gani.

760
00:58:33,132 --> 00:58:35,676
Wengine wote walidhani alikuwa siriazi sana...

761
00:58:36,344 --> 00:58:38,095
lakini kwangu, alikuwa mjinga-mjinga tu.

762
00:58:40,973 --> 00:58:42,016
Je, baba yako yuko hivyo...

763
00:58:43,726 --> 00:58:45,520
unajua, mnapokuwa wawili tu?

764
00:58:47,396 --> 00:58:48,397
Hapana.

765
00:58:51,484 --> 00:58:53,277
Nataka tu kuhakikisha
kuwa wewe ni jasiri vya kutosha.

766
00:58:54,529 --> 00:58:55,530
Kama yeye.

767
00:59:00,243 --> 00:59:01,744
Unajua, ninapotazama uso wako...

768
00:59:03,746 --> 00:59:05,373
Naona macho ya babu yako.

769
00:59:06,332 --> 00:59:07,333
Inapendeza.

770
00:59:12,672 --> 00:59:13,673
Kabisa.

771
00:59:26,811 --> 00:59:27,979
Unapaswa kulala kidogo.

772
00:59:30,064 --> 00:59:32,275
Nitabaki macho. Nitalinda.

773
00:59:32,775 --> 00:59:33,818
Sawa, Baba.

774
01:02:03,509 --> 01:02:04,510
Nini?

775
01:02:07,930 --> 01:02:09,056
Nini kimetokea?

776
01:02:10,558 --> 01:02:11,559
Sijui.

777
01:02:13,895 --> 01:02:14,896
Hapa.

778
01:02:17,940 --> 01:02:19,025
Lazima niende.

779
01:04:18,144 --> 01:04:19,604
Washenzi hawa wabaya.

780
01:04:21,814 --> 01:04:23,024
Sawa, rudi nyuma.

781
01:06:27,523 --> 01:06:28,524
Oho, tazama.

782
01:06:30,401 --> 01:06:31,402
Malaika yule.

783
01:06:33,154 --> 01:06:35,823
Unakumbuka mara ya kwanza uliponionyesha yule malaika, Baba?

784
01:06:38,910 --> 01:06:40,203
Tuliendesha gari hadi karibu na hapa.

785
01:06:41,370 --> 01:06:42,371
Tukaacha gari.

786
01:06:44,499 --> 01:06:47,668
Tulitembea mpaka tulipomwona akichomoza juu ya vilele vya miti.

787
01:06:49,295 --> 01:06:51,380
Ulisema atasimama hivi milele.

788
01:06:52,381 --> 01:06:55,175
Kama piramidi. Au Stonehenge.

789
01:06:55,176 --> 01:06:56,885
Kwa hiyo unapoitazama, una...

790
01:06:56,886 --> 01:06:59,638
Unatazama wakati ujao. Unaikumbuka siku hiyo?

791
01:06:59,639 --> 01:07:02,683
Sikuweza kuwa na zaidi ya miaka mingapi, saba au nane?

792
01:07:04,393 --> 01:07:07,313
Sisi wawili ni wasafiri halisi wa muda, ulisema.

793
01:07:09,690 --> 01:07:11,108
Tumeangukia katika siku zijazo.

794
01:07:13,069 --> 01:07:14,070
Na nika...

795
01:07:16,072 --> 01:07:17,073
Nikaogopa.

796
01:07:20,076 --> 01:07:23,788
Kwa sababu nilidhani ulikuwa unamaanisha na kweli tulikuwa tumefanya hivyo.

797
01:07:27,083 --> 01:07:29,335
Ni mamia mangapi ya miaka tumeporomoka safari hii?

798
01:07:31,587 --> 01:07:33,130
Ni maelfu au zaidi?

799
01:07:33,631 --> 01:07:34,799
Mama?

800
01:07:40,471 --> 01:07:41,763
Spike.

801
01:07:41,764 --> 01:07:43,558
Pua yako inatoka damu tena.

802
01:07:56,487 --> 01:07:57,738
Tulia.

803
01:07:59,282 --> 01:08:00,283
Usisogee.

804
01:08:03,369 --> 01:08:04,537
Tulia.

805
01:08:10,001 --> 01:08:12,253
Hapana, hapana, hapana! Subiri! Usipepese macho!

806
01:08:13,296 --> 01:08:14,297
Uko sawa.

807
01:08:20,094 --> 01:08:21,929
Jamani. Twende, Mama!

808
01:08:26,642 --> 01:08:28,102
Endelea, Mama!

809
01:08:30,771 --> 01:08:32,023
Usisimame!

810
01:08:37,445 --> 01:08:39,322
Kimbia! Kimbia!

811
01:08:42,200 --> 01:08:43,742
Usisimame, Mama! Ingia ndani!

812
01:08:43,743 --> 01:08:44,911
Nenda, Mama, nenda!

813
01:08:54,170 --> 01:08:55,963
Ingia ndani! Ingia ndani!

814
01:08:57,632 --> 01:08:58,965
Ingia ndani!

815
01:09:00,801 --> 01:09:02,386
Mavi! Mavi!

816
01:09:07,517 --> 01:09:09,602
Nenda! Ndani! Ingia!

817
01:09:11,228 --> 01:09:12,646
Spike, siwezi kupumua.

818
01:09:12,647 --> 01:09:14,232
Spike, ni gesi!

819
01:09:16,609 --> 01:09:17,943
- Can't breathe!
- No, Mum!

820
01:09:17,944 --> 01:09:19,027
- No, Mum!
- Don't...

821
01:09:29,038 --> 01:09:30,164
Get off her!

822
01:09:32,625 --> 01:09:33,625
Spike...

823
01:09:35,169 --> 01:09:36,170
Spikey!

824
01:09:37,713 --> 01:09:38,714
Get off her!

825
01:09:48,723 --> 01:09:49,891
Get down! Now!

826
01:09:49,892 --> 01:09:51,018
Go on!

827
01:10:39,525 --> 01:10:40,526
What happened?

828
01:10:42,945 --> 01:10:44,154
Benzene.

829
01:10:44,155 --> 01:10:45,239
Vaporised.

830
01:10:46,157 --> 01:10:47,366
Built up over the years.

831
01:10:52,455 --> 01:10:53,456
I'm Spike.

832
01:10:55,666 --> 01:10:56,918
And this is me mum.

833
01:10:58,961 --> 01:10:59,962
I'm Erik.

834
01:11:15,811 --> 01:11:16,812
What's wrong with her?

835
01:11:18,022 --> 01:11:19,023
I don't know.

836
01:11:20,733 --> 01:11:21,734
I'm taking her to a doctor.

837
01:11:24,237 --> 01:11:25,529
Right.

838
01:11:25,530 --> 01:11:26,614
What happens now?

839
01:11:27,782 --> 01:11:29,783
- What do you mean?
- Well, you live here, don't you?

840
01:11:29,784 --> 01:11:31,869
On this fucking island. You're a native.

841
01:11:32,453 --> 01:11:34,788
- Mwenyeji? - Hey, nini kinaendelea sasa hivi?

842
01:11:34,789 --> 01:11:36,122
Kuna waambukizwa wengine wanakuja?

843
01:11:36,123 --> 01:11:37,750
Sijui. Labda.

844
01:11:38,334 --> 01:11:40,294
 - Watakuwa wamesikia kelele. - Bila shaka, watakuja.

845
01:11:41,337 --> 01:11:42,546
<i>Bärsärk</i> atakuja.

846
01:11:42,547 --> 01:11:44,549
Watatung'oa vichwa vyetu kabisa. Unaelewa?

847
01:11:45,550 --> 01:11:47,426
 - Wewe si wa hapa. - Hebu mnyamazishe, tafadhali?

848
01:11:47,885 --> 01:11:49,094
Subiri, unatokea wapi?

849
01:11:49,095 --> 01:11:50,512
Natokea Sweden, sasa unaweza kumnyamazisha?

850
01:11:50,513 --> 01:11:52,722
 - Hawezi kujizuia. - Hawezi kujizuia?

851
01:11:52,723 --> 01:11:56,142
Huwezi kunisaidia? Kwa nini nikusaidie, jamani?

852
01:11:56,143 --> 01:11:58,062
Ningeweza kuokoa risasi zangu!

853
01:12:03,609 --> 01:12:04,693
Lazima niondoke hapa.

854
01:12:04,694 --> 01:12:06,821
 - Naondoka. - Basi, unaweza kwenda.

855
01:12:07,822 --> 01:12:08,947
Simwachi.

856
01:12:08,948 --> 01:12:11,033
Asante, Baba.

857
01:12:11,659 --> 01:12:13,953
Mungu wangu. Hali hii inaweza kuwa mbaya zaidi?

858
01:12:18,207 --> 01:12:19,417
Lahaula.

859
01:12:20,877 --> 01:12:24,255
Rafiki yangu mkuu wa shuleni ni dereva wa usafirishaji.

860
01:12:25,131 --> 01:12:27,425
Hujui dereva wa usafirishaji ni nini.

861
01:12:28,593 --> 01:12:29,718
Anasafirisha vifurushi.

862
01:12:29,719 --> 01:12:31,554
Unajua, watu huagiza vitu mtandaoni.

863
01:12:32,597 --> 01:12:34,222
Naamini hata hujui mtandaoni ni nini.

864
01:12:34,223 --> 01:12:35,557
Haijalishi.

865
01:12:35,558 --> 01:12:37,350
Ni dereva.

866
01:12:37,351 --> 01:12:38,977
Na nikamwambia...

867
01:12:38,978 --> 01:12:41,146
unapoteza maisha yako, Felix.

868
01:12:41,147 --> 01:12:44,525
Una maisha moja tu, na unayachezea.

869
01:12:45,985 --> 01:12:47,068
Naye akasema...

870
01:12:47,069 --> 01:12:49,322
"Yeah, utafanya nini, mpumbavu wewe?"

871
01:12:50,990 --> 01:12:52,200
Kwa hiyo nilijiunga na jeshi la majini...

872
01:12:53,201 --> 01:12:54,368
ili kuthibitisha jambo.

873
01:12:54,785 --> 01:12:56,412
Sasa ni nani anayechezea maisha yake, eh?

874
01:12:58,456 --> 01:12:59,748
Sielewi unachosema.

875
01:12:59,749 --> 01:13:01,917
Nasema nilipaswa kuwa dereva wa usafirishaji.

876
01:13:01,918 --> 01:13:05,420
Sasa hivi, ningekuwa nimekwama kwenye foleni mahali fulani...

877
01:13:05,421 --> 01:13:08,298
au nikiendesha kwa kasi sana kwenye barabara nyembamba au kitu kama hicho.

878
01:13:08,299 --> 01:13:09,425
Sasa mbona uko hapa?

879
01:13:10,092 --> 01:13:11,511
Boti yangu ya pumbavu ilizama.

880
01:13:13,179 --> 01:13:15,806
Tulikuwa tukishika doria kwenye pwani ya mashariki ya Scotland na tukagonga kitu.

881
01:13:17,266 --> 01:13:18,351
Scotch kwenye miamba.

882
01:13:20,353 --> 01:13:21,354
Haijalishi.

883
01:13:22,897 --> 01:13:24,232
Wachache wetu tulipata boti ya kuokea maisha.

884
01:13:24,774 --> 01:13:27,318
Hatukutaka kufika ufukweni, bila shaka, lakini upepo ulitupeleka.

885
01:13:28,236 --> 01:13:30,780
Nane kati yetu tulifika nchi kavu. Sasa mimi pekee ndiye niliyebaki.

886
01:13:31,822 --> 01:13:32,907
Je, utaokolewa?

887
01:13:35,576 --> 01:13:37,661
Unajua kuwa kisiwa chote kiko kwenye karantini, sivyo?

888
01:13:37,662 --> 01:13:39,455
Unadhani boti za doria ni za kazi gani?

889
01:13:40,039 --> 01:13:41,666
Naam, najua kuna karantini.

890
01:13:42,291 --> 01:13:43,834
Lakini nilidhani ni kwa ajili yetu tu.

891
01:13:43,835 --> 01:13:46,879
Karantini ni kwa ajili ya mnyonge yeyote anayekanyaga kisiwa hiki.

892
01:13:48,214 --> 01:13:49,674
Ukifika nchi kavu, huondoki tena.

893
01:13:53,845 --> 01:13:55,096
Unaweza kuja kwenye mji wangu.

894
01:13:55,721 --> 01:13:57,348
Baada ya kumpeleka mama yangu kwa daktari.

895
01:13:57,974 --> 01:13:59,559
Ndiyo, daktari huyu yuko wapi?

896
01:14:01,394 --> 01:14:02,603
Pale.

897
01:14:04,146 --> 01:14:05,147
Si mbali.

898
01:14:05,815 --> 01:14:06,982
"Si mbali"?

899
01:14:06,983 --> 01:14:09,402
Haya, haya, hebu jaribu kumbeba mama yako kwa muda.

900
01:14:10,862 --> 01:14:11,863
Nitapumzika kidogo.

901
01:14:19,120 --> 01:14:21,038
Mlo wa kwanza ndani ya siku moja na nusu.

902
01:14:24,792 --> 01:14:25,877
Chukua lingine.

903
01:14:29,088 --> 01:14:31,382
Inaonekana unapenda sana matofaa.

904
01:14:36,929 --> 01:14:37,930
Ndiyo.

905
01:14:38,764 --> 01:14:39,849
Asilimia moja.

906
01:14:41,392 --> 01:14:42,476
Hakuna mtandao.

907
01:14:46,314 --> 01:14:47,315
Hicho ni nini?

908
01:14:49,483 --> 01:14:50,775
Hivi punde, litakuwa tofali.

909
01:14:50,776 --> 01:14:53,612
Lakini kwa muda mchache zaidi ni...

910
01:14:53,613 --> 01:14:55,280
kitu kama redio.

911
01:14:55,281 --> 01:14:56,365
Lakini chenye picha.

912
01:14:57,617 --> 01:14:58,618
Je, mna redio?

913
01:15:00,411 --> 01:15:01,412
Je, mna picha?

914
01:15:02,705 --> 01:15:03,998
Baadhi ya watu wana za zamani.

915
01:15:06,375 --> 01:15:08,377
Hapo. Itazame hiyo.

916
01:15:09,253 --> 01:15:10,254
Hiyo ni mpya.

917
01:15:12,465 --> 01:15:13,632
Huyu ni mchumba wangu.

918
01:15:13,633 --> 01:15:14,759
Au wa zamani...

919
01:15:15,343 --> 01:15:16,344
Nadhani.

920
01:15:17,470 --> 01:15:18,596
Uso wake una nini?

921
01:15:19,388 --> 01:15:20,431
Unamaanisha nini?

922
01:15:21,516 --> 01:15:22,558
Anaonekana wa ajabu.

923
01:15:23,100 --> 01:15:24,351
Wewe ndiye wa ajabu.

924
01:15:24,352 --> 01:15:25,937
Ni mrembo sana. Una nini wewe?

925
01:15:26,646 --> 01:15:27,938
Najua ni nini.

926
01:15:27,939 --> 01:15:30,148
Kuna msichana mmoja mjini kwetu
ambaye ana tatizo hilihili. neighborhood. 

927
01:15:30,149 --> 01:15:32,818
- Tatizo?
- Ana mzio wa vyakula vya baharini. 

928
01:15:33,653 --> 01:15:35,445
Kwa hiyo, akila chaza, basi...

929
01:15:35,446 --> 01:15:36,738
mdomo wake wote unanenepa sana 

930
01:15:36,739 --> 01:15:38,324
- na kuvimba.
- Nipe hicho.

931
01:15:40,952 --> 01:15:42,203
Ndiyo, ndiyo huyo.

932
01:15:46,833 --> 01:15:48,543
Usijihusishe na Felix.

933
01:15:51,212 --> 01:15:52,213
Baba...

934
01:15:52,797 --> 01:15:53,798
Nina baridi.

935
01:16:01,222 --> 01:16:02,557
Mbona anakuita "Baba"?

936
01:16:03,850 --> 01:16:05,101
Hiyo ni ajabu.

937
01:16:05,852 --> 01:16:08,938
Namaanisha, nina uhakika kuna ndoa nyingi za ndugu sehemu hizi...

938
01:16:10,231 --> 01:16:12,942
lakini hii inaonekana haiwezekani.

939
01:16:14,026 --> 01:16:15,152
Amechanganyikiwa tu.

940
01:16:15,945 --> 01:16:17,445
Hakuwa hivi siku zote.

941
01:16:17,446 --> 01:16:19,906
Muda mwingi yuko vile alivyokuwa siku zote.

942
01:16:19,907 --> 01:16:21,325
Nani yuko vile alivyokuwa siku zote?

943
01:16:24,245 --> 01:16:25,246
Wewe, Mama.

944
01:16:34,172 --> 01:16:35,256
Wewe ni nani?

945
01:16:36,424 --> 01:16:37,425
Mimi ni Erik.

946
01:16:39,177 --> 01:16:40,595
Na huyu ni baba yako, Spike.

947
01:16:42,180 --> 01:16:43,430
Nini?

948
01:16:43,431 --> 01:16:45,223
Anatania tu, Mama.

949
01:16:45,224 --> 01:16:46,725
Anazingua.

950
01:16:46,726 --> 01:16:47,809
Mama!

951
01:16:47,810 --> 01:16:49,060
Samahani.

